<div class="info">
  <h3>Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>(2 or 3) Pump Control Center</li>
    <li>Compartmentalized design</li>
    <li>24Volt PCP</li>
    <li>Lightning protection (TVSS)</li>
    <li>Transfer Switch with status panel</li>
    <li>120V branch breakers</li>
    <li>Motor circuit breakers with lockout provisions</li>
    <li>Motor starters (FVNR, RVSS, or AFD)</li>
    <li>Pump overtemp &amp; seal monitoring</li>
    <li>User-friendly automatic pump controller &#038; back up float controls</li>
    <li>Field Terminal connection compartment with fingersafe lugs</li>
    <li>Thermostatically controlled electric heater</li>
    <li>GFCI convenience outlet</li>
    <li>Overall height fits beneath standard commercial doorways</li>
    <li>Rigid steel with white painted exterior</li>
    <li>Engraved nameplates for easy identification</li>
  </ul>
</div>

